snippet.title: Motivator Network
snippet.description:
Direct Help Network & Motivators. 2 Way Success: Directly helping, motivators, House Network, help requests - Integrating into Worldie.com!

Promote helping people, motivation, defending others, survival, self-defense, anti-crime, resilience, inspiration, and charity. 

We support causes, victims, prevention, and rescue projects. Duty to rescue and duty to care policies are advocated for. Interference and influence online with examples shows proof of its positive social effects.

Focus on positivism, solutions, and change!

Our mission is to change the paradigm that people cannot help directly. We encourage people to think in a more innovative way. We want to create a new community of people who encourage others to help and motivate.

Fight environmental, societal, & relational issues which de-motivate. Do humanitarian & social change. 

We aim to improve success, independence, action, self-sufficiency, self-defense, resilience, innovation, and empowerment.

Challenge the status quo!
